high_descs: Turn right and walk to the small table with the plant on it.
Take one bar of soap from the table.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the bar of soap in the sink and turn the water on, shut the water off and get the soap from the sink.
Turn right and face the toilet in the corner.
Put the soap on the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Put the rinsed bar of soap on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn around to the black table.
Pick up the bar of soap from the front of the black table.
Carry the soap and turn around to find the sink.
Place the soap in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the soap.
Hold the soap and face to the right.
Place the soap on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a bar of soap and place it on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Go past the tub on the right to the small table.
Pick up a bar of soap on the table near the front edge.
Turn and go to the sink across the room.
Turn around and go to the sink.
rinse off the soap in the sink.
Turn to the right and put the rinsed soap on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap on the back of the toilet.
